	Use the VCSN_EMPTY macro.
	* ../../../../include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg_graph_impl.hxx:
	Fix a wrong parameter passed to a method.
	* ../../../../tools/vcsn-graph-util: Update script name in help output.

