2007-12-10  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Introduce new types for delta containers.
	In order to use the full potential of the bmi structure, I need
	to make the delta containers dependent on the graph structure.
	I also need to make a distinction between const and non-const
	delta. The 4 followings types have been introduced:
	- delta_transition_t
	- delta_state_t
	- const_delta_transition_t
	- const_delta_state_t
	This patch doesn't use these types everywhere. More patches
	will come later.

	Delta functions using an insertIterator instead of a container
	have also been removed since we do want the graph to handle both
	the delta containers AND the insertion way.

	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/accessible.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/complete.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/determinize.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/eps_removal.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/minimization_hopcroft.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/minimization_moore.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/misc/usual_macros.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/tools/fsm_dump.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/tools/gen_random.hxx,
	* src/tests/include/tests/automata/implementation_check/rdelta_test.hh:
	Make use of the new types.

	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/automata_base.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/automata_base.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/automata_ops.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/automata_ops.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/transpose_view.hh: 
	Remove useless delta functions.

	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg/boostg_delta_state.hh:
	New. Introduce a new container to store non-const delta results and...

	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg/boostg_functors.hh:
	...add the proper functor.

	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg_graph_impl.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg_graph_impl.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/legacy_graph_impl.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/legacy_graph_impl.hxx:
	Declare the new types and update the delta functions prototype.
	
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg/graphcontainer.hh: reindent.

2007-11-29  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix incompatibility with GCC 4.1.1. 
	* concept/smart_label.hh: for some reasons, GCC 4.1.1 did not resolved
	templated functions correctly when a tag, passed as template parameter,
	was declared in a templated struct.
	Thanks to this patch Vaucanson compiles with GCC 4.x.

