	specified in the for_all* macros.

2007-11-23  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Add new for_all_* macros. 
	* vaucanson/misc/usual_macros.hh:
	Since we will be able to use various automata structures in a same
	function, we need to specify which types of which automaton we are
	currently using when iterating over a container for instance.
	AUTOMATON_TYPES* allowed that but not the for_all_* macros.
	It's fixed.

2007-11-23  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Remove a non-standard operator in Support. 
	* vaucanson/misc/support.hh: Remove the operator.
	* vaucanson/xml/tools.hxx: Fix the code using it.
	Support containers had operator*() which returned the first
	element value of the container if there was only one element.
	Since it is not STL compliant I removed it.

